"{\"uid\": \"independent.co.uk-sport-olympics-simone-biles-twisties-olympics-gymnastics-paris-b2588361.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Notifications can be managed in browser preferences.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 52, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in  Swipe for next article  The American returns to the Olympics after struggling to perform at Tokyo 2020 due to the condition  Removed from bookmarks  I would like to be emailed about offers, events and updates from The Independent.\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 422, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 220, \"end\": 228, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999787319117562, \"rank\": 2.1234503309392214e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 284, \"end\": 289, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.959396921995886, \"rank\": 0.042305163787951114, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice  Simone Bilesreturns to theOlympicsatParis 2024after suffering from the twisties in Tokyo three years ago, eventually leading toa 732-day layoff from the sport.\", \"from\": 423, \"to\": 606, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 530, \"end\": 535, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.959396921995886, \"rank\": 0.042305163787951114, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles promises to be the star ofthe gymnastics in Parisand hopes to avoid the twisties this time.\", \"from\": 608, \"to\": 705, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The condition, usually in high-pressure situations such as the Olympics or world championships, involves losing control midair and feeling unable to land the move, creating a high-risk and dangerous situation.\", \"from\": 706, \"to\": 915, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It has been likened to the yips in golf or baseball, where professionals suddenly lose the ability to perform under pressure.\", \"from\": 917, \"to\": 1042, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles has described the feeling of the phenomenon as being \\\"lost in the air.\\\"\", \"from\": 1044, \"to\": 1121, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She then likened the uncomfortable experience to being unable to drive while at the wheel in a car: \\\"Your mind and your body are at a disconnect.\", \"from\": 1122, \"to\": 1267, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Your body is going to try to do something, and your mind is going to be like, 'No, you are not doing this', I am my car.\\\"\", \"from\": 1268, \"to\": 1389, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles first noticed a problem and a sense of instability while practicing her vault before Team USA's first gymnastics rotation in 2021.\", \"from\": 1391, \"to\": 1527, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1482, \"end\": 1490, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.995525232808327, \"rank\": 0.004187737027657129, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It does not feel comfortable, I have no idea where I am, but I am twisting, praying I land on my feet,\\\" Biles said on the the podcast Call Her Daddy.\", \"from\": 1528, \"to\": 1678, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I felt like I was fighting my body and my mind to do these tricks.\\\"\", \"from\": 1679, \"to\": 1747, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She knew she had the twisties but tried to 'push past that.'\\\"\", \"from\": 1748, \"to\": 1809, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles then changed the difficulty of her rotation from a 2.5 to 1.5 midair, correcting her body position to avoid an accident.\", \"from\": 1811, \"to\": 1937, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Rumours spread as to why Biles had struggled, but the athlete insisted it was not a physical issue: \\\"No, no injury, thankfully.\", \"from\": 1938, \"to\": 2065, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And that's why I took a step back, because I did not want to do something silly out there and get injured.\\\"\", \"from\": 2066, \"to\": 2173, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles is far from the only gymnast to experience the twisties, with former USA teammate Aleah Finnegan revealing that she first suffered from it as a child: \\\"I have had the twisties since I was 11.\", \"from\": 2175, \"to\": 2372, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2250, \"end\": 2253, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999135064008795, \"rank\": 8.227115228890145e-05, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 2263, \"end\": 2277, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aleah_Finnegan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Aleah Finnegan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aleah_Finnegan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aleah_Finnegan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I cannot imagine the fear of having it happen to you during competition.\\\"\", \"from\": 2373, \"to\": 2446, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While Laurie Hernandez, a teammate of Biles in 2016, also experienced it: \\\"I have had the twisties before.\", \"from\": 2448, \"to\": 2554, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2454, \"end\": 2470, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurie_Hernandez\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Laurie Hernandez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurie_Hernandez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurie_Hernandez\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hated it - so much.\", \"from\": 2555, \"to\": 2574, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's painful.\", \"from\": 2575, \"to\": 2588, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It actively makes you feel like you are not the caliber of athlete that you are.\\\"\", \"from\": 2589, \"to\": 2670, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles was contending with a lot of stress and other psychological factors in the build-up to the Tokyo Olympics.\", \"from\": 2672, \"to\": 2784, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"(The pressure) feels heavy.\", \"from\": 2786, \"to\": 2814, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's like the weight of the world on your shoulders and I am very small, so I feel like, at times, it's very overwhelming,\\\" she explained.\", \"from\": 2815, \"to\": 2953, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But whenever you get so overwhelmed and have triggers, it's just like - I have to focus on my mental wellbeing and that's what I did.\\\"\", \"from\": 2954, \"to\": 3089, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To overcome the twisties, many gymnasts simplify their routine and build back up to the harder techniques.\", \"from\": 3091, \"to\": 3197, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Removing an element of risk can also remove the condition, such as performing the routine or technique into a foam pit.\", \"from\": 3199, \"to\": 3318, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It can suddenly return, but Biles dismissed doubts last year, stating: \\\"I am fine.\", \"from\": 3320, \"to\": 3402, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am twisting again.\", \"from\": 3403, \"to\": 3423, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"No worries.\", \"from\": 3424, \"to\": 3435, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All is good.\\\"\", \"from\": 3436, \"to\": 3449, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Join thought-provoking conversations, follow other Independent readers and see their replies  Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 3451, \"to\": 3681, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3502, \"end\": 3513, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.401684516329113e-19, \"text\": \"Independent\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\"}]}]}"